track.name: Give Your Heart Away
comments: Um....whatever just came up...it is NOT The Black Keys!  It's not bad, but it is most definitely not Black Keys.  Weird.
This song makes me want to listen to Cochise.
God, I forgot how good that riff is.
If you like these guys, give Junior Kimsborough a listen to see who may have influenced them a little!
:)  not there best album    but still a  shout
man i love this so much : )
Still my favorite album from these guys.
That riff would make Jimmy Page proud.
Reminds me at good old Jimi Hendrix
it's not that this track doesn't sound good.  there's just nothing outstanding about it....nothing new
The Black keys rock, I don't think these boys have  ever produced a bad track. seeing them live is pure Inspiration.
